data.description: Move right into this East Dearborn 3-bedroom 2 1/2 bath bungalow with covered porch and wide driveway. Open Living and Dining room. Kitchen features granite countertops, stainless steel appliances and ceramic tile. This fully finished basement features full kitchen and full bathroom, bonus room, and laundry room. The spacious upstairs bedroom has a walk-in closet and bathroom. The back yard is fenced in with a shed and paver patio.  Located within walking distance from West Warren commercial business district. Near Maples Elementary. Dearborn High school district. Immediate occupancy!
